@startuml quiz_flow_sequence
actor Student
participant App
participant "Quiz Service" as Quiz
participant DB

Student -> App : Start quiz
App -> Quiz : getQuestions()
Quiz -> DB : fetch questions
DB --> Quiz : questions
Quiz --> App : questions

Student -> App : Submit answers
App -> Quiz : evaluate()
Quiz -> DB : save result
Quiz --> App : score
App --> Student : Show result
@enduml